  • Type Parameters:
    O - The type of the elements of the input and of the elements of the output of a fanout neuron.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFluentObject<FanoutNeuron<O>>

    public final class FanoutNeuron<O>
extends Neuronoid<FanoutNeuron<O>,java.lang.Iterable<O>,java.lang.Iterable<O>>
    A fanout neuron is a neuron that: -Has a container of elements as input. -Can create fan neurons that have a single element as output.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
